Enum ETask

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ETask>
public enum ETask
extends Enum<ETask>

ETask defines the enumerations of all ITask.

The enumeration of an ITask implies the execution logic type of the ITask.
